                            "termAccession": ""
                        },
                        "description": "Plasma samples were obtained according to Indivumed standard operating procedures: EDTA-plasma was separated from the entire blood by a density gradient centrifugation using the Ficoll-Paque and a Leucosep Tube allowing also the separation of the mononuclear cells lymphocytes used for other aims. Plasma samples were stored at -80 \u00b0C until analysis.",
